      <section>
        <title>Export difficulties</title>
          <chapter>
            <paragraph>
              The economic problems of Finland came primarily from a drop in demand from Russia,
              first market for the Finnish export. Difficulties of trade have worsened by: the decline
              of its most successful company, Nokia together with the sector of the production of the paper.
            </paragraph>
            <paragraph>
              In numbers, export from finland to russia between 2008 and 2016 is fall of 33%.
            </paragraph>
